query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 0 AND q.favorite_count <= 10000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('datatable',
'delegates',
'django-forms',
'extjs',
'google-api',
'google-app-engine',
'numbers',
'promise',
'python-3.x',
'svn',
'tdd',
'typescript',
'uitableview',
'x86');
